description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'Core + Cardio Circuit ' from the channel Peter Donohoe.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Rower and Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Competitor and The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe.
The The Competitor vibe means Gamified, leaderboard-driven, full-send energy. This is especially good for Those who need to chase a score or beat their own record. The The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe means Beat-driven, strong but fluid, music-infused. This is especially good for When you want strength and rhythm to blend seamlessly..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Total body work off Hydrow and 90-second intervals on Hydrow. 

Max rhythm: 24, Format: Circuit...
